para_trans: Regarding declaration of appointing authority for direct service, promotion and deputation of Group-B (Non-Gazetted), Group-C and Group-D cadre employees of the Land Records Department.
Government Decision, No. Aastha-1225 / Q. No.461 / Aastha-6
Madam Cama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Reference: - General Administration Department, Government Decisions, No. SRV-2016 / Q. No.290 / Works. 12, D. 19.11.2016

Preamble: - The Department of General Administration, under the Government Decision in Reference, has directed the respective Administrative Departments to declare the post-wise appointment authority designation under separate orders as to who will be the appointing authority to take the final decision on the matters of direct service, promotion and appointment / posting of Group-B (non-gazetted) Group-C and Group-D posts.
Accordingly, the issue of declaring an appointing authority for Group-B (non-gazetted) Group-C and Group-D employees of the Land Records Department was under consideration of the Government.

Government Decision: - The Government is approving the declaration of the posts in Group-B (Non-Gazetted) Group-C and Group-D of the Land Records Department as "Appointment Authority" as mentioned in No. 4 of the following prospectus to take a final decision on the matters of appointments / postings to be made by direct service, promotion and deputation.
table_trans: Commissioner and Director of Land Records (M. State), Pune
Commissioner and Director of Land Records (M. State), Pune

para_trans: Government Decision Number: Aastha-1225 / Q. No.461 / Aastha-6

The appointing authority as declared above shall be for making final decisions on matters of direct service, promotion and appointment / posting to be made by deputation. However, the final decision regarding the transfer will be taken by the competent authority declared under the Transfer Act.

This Government Decision is being issued in accordance with the powers conferred on the Administrative Departments under the General Administration Department, Government Decision, No. SRV-2016 / Q. 290 / ACTION 12 dated 19.11.2016.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
